### What I can always do

I can write the addon code directly in chat:

```text
__init__.py
providers/rna_provider.py
providers/operator_provider.py
...
```

either:

* file-by-file
* module-by-module
* complete addon version-by-version

This is the most reliable approach because you can review every file before integrating it.

