If the environment supports file creation, I can generate:

```text
unisearch/
    __init__.py
    core/
    providers/
    resolver/
    ...
```

and package it into:

```text
unisearch.zip
```

then provide a downloadable file.

However, I only know that is possible when the tooling for the current conversation exposes file-generation capabilities.

